channel.title: Neonscape 317 Server (Unleashed Download)
channel.description:
Hellow and I am Thunder418 and I am releasing my first new server named Neonscape, the reason I am releasing my server it's because I can no longer run stuff or compile stuff so I can't play my server no more therefore I will just release it to you guys and you can code it how ever you want :D
Items: HAS LOTS OF COSTUMS ITEMS, Shops are coded by me and I have coded the stats for items as well you can change that how ever you want to change it your (choice) Ex: Has Godswords,Barrows,D Claws, and lots of costums as I said already hope you enjoy it!
Pics: [IMG]http://i48.tinypic.com/s1mgyr.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i45.tinypic.com/2e4w708.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i49.tinypic.com/1khu9.jpg[/img] This Were Pics from before when I had the Server I know their not good, but oh well you can check out server your self.
Credits:70% Me of Server&Client, 10% my friend for helping me create the client, 20% Delta.
Downloads: Server (source) Download: http://uppit.com/v/QV3XTP39 Client Download: http://uppit.com/v/F39LO04L
If you are having trouble like when it's about to open the download page it takes you somewhere else... try refreshing the page one more time alright. :D
